r4052 | fenrir | 2003-04-13 22:00:21 +0200 (Sun, 13 Apr 2003) | 19 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/configure.ac.in
   M /trunk/include/input_ext-intf.h
   M /trunk/include/stream_output.h
   M /trunk/include/vlc_common.h
