r5627 | nitrox | 2003-11-06 17:36:41 +0100 (Thu, 06 Nov 2003) | 22 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/configure.ac
   M /trunk/include/codecs.h
   M /trunk/include/input_ext-dec.h
